00:25:09,680 --> 00:25:10,480
Really?

572
00:25:16,160 --> 00:25:17,790
It's quite cold here at night.

573
00:25:17,830 --> 00:25:19,200
You're still injured.

574
00:25:19,300 --> 00:25:20,540
Let's go back first.

575
00:25:21,960 --> 00:25:22,600
Alright.

576
00:25:27,000 --> 00:25:27,790
Come on.

577
00:25:40,480 --> 00:25:41,350
You've forgotten.

578
00:25:41,680 --> 00:25:43,160
I have a mechanical bird that can fly.

579
00:25:43,640 --> 00:25:45,240
No one can stop me.

580
00:25:46,960 --> 00:25:48,000
Heaven and Earth are the primal source, from which all energies arise.

581
00:25:48,000 --> 00:25:49,350
Born of deep wisdom, all things return to their origin.

582
00:25:49,350 --> 00:25:50,510
Yandu, gather!

583
00:26:52,480 --> 00:26:54,640
How are you feeling? Better?

584
00:26:59,160 --> 00:27:00,030
Much better.

585
00:27:00,680 --> 00:27:01,720
After applying the medicine a few more times,

586
00:27:01,720 --> 00:27:02,310
your eyes

587
00:27:02,310 --> 00:27:03,680
will recover soon.

588
00:27:05,440 --> 00:27:06,510
I'll head back now.

589
00:27:07,110 --> 00:27:08,590
I woke up early this morning

590
00:27:08,590 --> 00:27:10,440
just to avoid Curly.

591
00:27:10,880 --> 00:27:11,830
Don't worry.

592
00:27:12,440 --> 00:27:14,070
Actually, Curly is even more timid.

593
00:27:14,590 --> 00:27:16,440
Her personality is a bit strange.

594
00:27:16,590 --> 00:27:17,750
Has she always been like this?

595
00:27:18,920 --> 00:27:19,790
I suppose so.

596
00:27:20,440 --> 00:27:21,240
Curly

597
00:27:21,920 --> 00:27:23,750
was born into a large family.

598
00:27:24,590 --> 00:27:26,030
We've known each other since childhood.

599
00:27:27,750 --> 00:27:29,680
While others could transform in about 10 years,

600
00:27:30,200 --> 00:27:31,070
it took her

601
00:27:31,590 --> 00:27:32,960
50 years.

602
00:27:33,680 --> 00:27:35,030
We all thought

603
00:27:35,160 --> 00:27:36,790
she wouldn't be able to transform at all.

604
00:27:37,160 --> 00:27:38,400
The Youhu Clan

605
00:27:38,400 --> 00:27:39,680
is generally laid-back in personality,

606
00:27:40,310 --> 00:27:42,880
with our fair share of bad habits,

607
00:27:44,000 --> 00:27:45,350
but Curly's habits

608
00:27:45,820 --> 00:27:46,820
seem even stranger.

609
00:27:47,720 --> 00:27:48,510
Reclusive?

610
00:28:02,640 --> 00:28:03,640
Yes, and her fur is different.

611
00:28:04,310 --> 00:28:05,960
While others have smooth, straight fur,

612
00:28:06,480 --> 00:28:07,270
hers

613
00:28:07,830 --> 00:28:08,750
is curly.

614
00:28:09,000 --> 00:28:09,920
Because of this,

615
00:28:10,680 --> 00:28:12,400
she's often the subject of ridicule.

616
00:28:12,680 --> 00:28:13,550
As for her,

617
00:28:14,240 --> 00:28:15,350
she couldn't fight back,

618
00:28:16,110 --> 00:28:17,240
always getting the short end of the stick.

619
00:28:17,310 --> 00:28:18,750
Over time,

620
00:28:18,790 --> 00:28:20,240
she developed the habit of avoiding people whenever possible.

621
00:28:20,720 --> 00:28:22,640
But her skill in barrier magic

622
00:28:22,640 --> 00:28:23,590
is impressive.

623
00:28:23,790 --> 00:28:25,480
She's the type who learned it all on her own, without a teacher.

624
00:28:25,750 --> 00:28:27,640
She often uses her barrier magic

625
00:28:27,830 --> 00:28:29,110
to hide herself away.

626
00:28:29,270 --> 00:28:31,110
The whole family will search for her for days,

627
00:28:31,180 --> 00:28:32,370
but she just won't come out.

628
00:28:47,200 --> 00:28:49,160
It might be because she's upset or angry.

629
00:28:49,720 --> 00:28:50,750
Sometimes that's true,

630
00:28:51,640 --> 00:28:52,640
but most of the time,

631
00:28:53,030 --> 00:28:54,070
it's simply because there are too many people,

632
00:28:55,030 --> 00:28:56,000
and she finds it annoying.

633
00:28:59,440 --> 00:29:00,590
I see.

634
00:29:00,960 --> 00:29:02,110
So after she transformed,

635
00:29:02,350 --> 00:29:03,640
she stopped talking.

636
00:29:04,510 --> 00:29:06,070
It wasn't until she got a pet

637
00:29:06,680 --> 00:29:08,030
that she gradually started to improve.

638
00:29:53,110 --> 00:29:55,350
Curly's life is very structured.

639
00:29:56,350 --> 00:29:57,160
Four,

640
00:29:57,270 --> 00:29:58,070
three,

641
00:29:58,510 --> 00:29:59,310
two,

642
00:29:59,780 --> 00:30:00,580
one.

643
00:30:13,550 --> 00:30:14,960
She doesn't want to learn

644
00:30:15,310 --> 00:30:16,350
the clan's methods of cultivation.

645
00:30:17,200 --> 00:30:18,960
While she excels at Barrier Spell,

646
00:30:19,000 --> 00:30:20,350
no one else in the clan can do it,

647
00:30:20,960 --> 00:30:22,240
which is why

648
00:30:22,270 --> 00:30:23,160
she relies on

649
00:30:23,160 --> 00:30:24,640
breathing techniques

650
00:30:24,920 --> 00:30:26,160
to absorb spiritual energy

651
00:30:26,160 --> 00:30:27,200
at noon.

652
00:30:35,110 --> 00:30:36,590
The midday sun holds the essence of fire,

653
00:30:36,780 --> 00:30:38,650
containing the sun's true flames.

654
00:30:39,720 --> 00:30:42,680
It's the purest, most potent energy, burning through everything.

655
00:30:43,240 --> 00:30:45,590
Especially at noon,

656
00:30:45,960 --> 00:30:47,920
when the sun is at its peak.

657
00:30:48,640 --> 00:30:50,270
If she continues

658
00:30:50,270 --> 00:30:51,750
to absorb its energy,

659
00:30:52,030 --> 00:30:52,830
she may eventually

660
00:30:53,790 --> 00:30:56,640
achieve enlightenment and become a god.

661
00:30:59,240 --> 00:31:00,850
How do you know all of this?

662
00:31:05,000 --> 00:31:06,550
I... My master taught me.

663
00:31:07,200 --> 00:31:09,510
You know, he's really powerful.

664
00:31:14,960 --> 00:31:15,750
Maybe.

665
00:31:16,720 --> 00:31:17,590
She always says

666
00:31:18,000 --> 00:31:19,750
the spiritual energy she absorbs at noon

667
00:31:20,110 --> 00:31:20,920
is the sweetest

668
00:31:21,790 --> 00:31:22,880
and the most comfortable.

669
00:31:26,290 --> 00:31:27,100
By the way,

670
00:31:27,550 --> 00:31:29,160
she wrote a letter to us.

671
00:31:29,920 --> 00:31:31,110
I can't read it.

672
00:31:31,750 --> 00:31:32,830
I'll read it to you.

673
00:31:36,920 --> 00:31:38,030
I'll wake up at 9 a.m.

674
00:31:38,270 --> 00:31:40,270
Before then, I'll be asleep,

675
00:31:40,830 --> 00:31:42,030
so please keep quiet.

676
00:31:42,830 --> 00:31:43,920
At 9 a.m. sharp,

677
00:31:44,090 --> 00:31:47,240
I'll wash up and come out to fetch water.

678
00:31:47,600 --> 00:31:48,430
At 9:30 a.m...

679
00:31:48,510 --> 00:31:49,240
Enough.

680
00:31:49,880 --> 00:31:52,030
I know her routine well.

681
00:31:54,750 --> 00:31:55,960
She's reminding us

682
00:31:55,960 --> 00:31:57,240
not to come out carelessly,

683
00:31:57,310 --> 00:31:58,960
to avoid running into her.

684
00:31:59,750 --> 00:32:01,240
She was the same

685
00:32:01,510 --> 00:32:02,680
back at Fangwai Mountain,

686
00:32:03,680 --> 00:32:05,200
but no one really paid attention to it.

687
00:32:05,880 --> 00:32:07,000
Still, you don't need to worry about her.

688
00:32:07,880 --> 00:32:08,880
That's not right.

689
00:32:10,030 --> 00:32:12,200
After all, we're at her place,

690
00:32:12,200 --> 00:32:12,750
and we should

691
00:32:12,750 --> 00:32:14,070
respect her rules.

692
00:32:14,160 --> 00:32:14,960
Besides,

693
00:32:15,000 --> 00:32:16,550
she mostly stays in her room

694
00:32:16,550 --> 00:32:17,720
and doesn't come out.

695
00:32:17,880 --> 00:32:18,750
Honestly,

696
00:32:19,240 --> 00:32:20,960
it's not an inconvenience at all.

697
00:32:21,680 --> 00:32:22,480
Alright.

698
00:32:24,720 --> 00:32:25,960
Is that the reason

699
00:32:26,110 --> 00:32:27,720
she left Fangwai Mountain?

700
00:32:30,790 --> 00:32:32,000
The situation back then

701
00:32:32,000 --> 00:32:33,400
was much more complicated.

702
00:32:34,750 --> 00:32:35,590
At the time,

703
00:32:36,070 --> 00:32:38,030
the War Demons and the Youhu Clan were already in conflict.

704
00:32:39,110 --> 00:32:41,240
Curly's father was a general in the War Division.

705
00:32:41,550 --> 00:32:43,270
Even though he knew about Curly's condition,

706
00:32:43,880 --> 00:32:44,720
he still forced her

707
00:32:44,720 --> 00:32:45,790
to join the battlefield.

708
00:32:46,270 --> 00:32:47,550
It wasn't due to a lack of soldiers,

709
00:32:48,000 --> 00:32:49,000
but because

710
00:32:49,200 --> 00:32:50,070
he wanted her to be an example

711
00:32:50,070 --> 00:32:51,200
for the clan.

712
00:32:52,480 --> 00:32:54,000
As you can imagine,

713
00:32:54,390 --> 00:32:56,980
Curly's condition only worsened.

714
00:32:57,550 --> 00:32:58,440
If I hadn't secretly

715
00:32:58,440 --> 00:32:59,590
rescued her,

716
00:33:00,270 --> 00:33:01,160
she might have

717
00:33:01,750 --> 00:33:03,550
already lost her sanity by now.

718
00:33:08,790 --> 00:33:10,550
I should have been more considerate toward her.

719
00:33:27,310 --> 00:33:28,720
Why aren't you following the rules?

720
00:33:28,830 --> 00:33:29,920
It's noon now,

721
00:33:29,920 --> 00:33:30,510
which means it's clearly my time

722
00:33:30,510 --> 00:33:31,830
to be out and about.

723
00:33:42,480 --> 00:33:43,350
How's it going?

724
00:33:44,960 --> 00:33:45,750
Look,

725
00:33:45,970 --> 00:33:47,250
the float is broken.

726
00:33:49,400 --> 00:33:50,830
It should be 1 p.m. now,

727
00:33:51,350 --> 00:33:52,510
not noon.

728
00:34:00,750 --> 00:34:01,920
I knew it.

729
00:34:02,110 --> 00:34:02,830
I've been feeling

730
00:34:02,830 --> 00:34:04,270
a bit off lately.

731
00:34:04,400 --> 00:34:06,270
I thought I was getting sick.

732
00:34:06,870 --> 00:34:07,630
Don't worry.

733
00:34:07,660 --> 00:34:09,070
I can fix it for you.

734
00:34:09,320 --> 00:34:10,110
You?

735
00:34:10,489 --> 00:34:11,230
Of course.

736
00:34:17,280 --> 00:34:18,110
It's all fixed.

737
00:34:19,739 --> 00:34:20,739
It's fixed?

738
00:34:21,510 --> 00:34:22,550
That was quick!

739
00:34:25,040 --> 00:34:25,929
Quick indeed.

740
00:34:26,510 --> 00:34:27,840
You're amazing!

741
00:34:30,960 --> 00:34:31,880
Here, take it.

742
00:34:34,670 --> 00:34:35,920
What's this?

743
00:34:35,920 --> 00:34:37,440
It's a bamboo dragonfly I made.

744
00:34:38,190 --> 00:34:39,710
Does it actually fly?

745
00:34:39,710 --> 00:34:40,760
Of course it does.

746
00:34:44,670 --> 00:34:46,000
What book are you reading?

747
00:34:49,159 --> 00:34:50,250
"Legend of Immortals."

748
00:34:50,670 --> 00:34:52,440
It tells the story of a remarkable woman

749
00:34:52,440 --> 00:34:54,630
who, on the fifteenth of July at 7 a.m.,

750
00:34:54,630 --> 00:34:56,480
with purple clouds swirling in the sky,

751
00:34:56,719 --> 00:34:57,840
flags and banners waving,

752
00:34:58,150 --> 00:34:59,030
and everyone watching,

753
00:34:59,030 --> 00:35:00,110
saw her soar towards the heavens,

754
00:35:00,110 --> 00:35:01,320
rising higher and higher,

755
00:35:01,400 --> 00:35:02,920
until she entered the Divine Realm

756
00:35:02,960 --> 00:35:04,880
and became a god.

757
00:35:05,590 --> 00:35:06,670
But this is just a fictional tale,

758
00:35:06,670 --> 00:35:08,000
dreamed up by someone.

759
00:35:08,110 --> 00:35:09,440
It shouldn't be taken literally.

760
00:35:10,150 --> 00:35:11,800
Why can't it be true?

761
00:35:11,800 --> 00:35:12,670
It clearly describes

762
00:35:12,670 --> 00:35:14,710
how she ascended

763
00:35:14,710 --> 00:35:15,760
to become a god.

764
00:35:16,190 --> 00:35:17,630
The Divine Realm is not in the sky,

765
00:35:17,840 --> 00:35:19,110
and the difference between the Divine Realm and the Mortal Realm

766
00:35:19,230 --> 00:35:20,800
is not a matter of distance,

767
00:35:21,070 --> 00:35:22,510
but of entirely separate worlds.

768
00:35:24,670 --> 00:35:26,320
Have you heard of the Heavenly Ladder?

769
00:35:29,670 --> 00:35:30,760
In the past, the Heavenly Ladder

770
00:35:30,760 --> 00:35:32,320
was the passage between the two realms.

771
00:35:33,510 --> 00:35:34,840
But now, the passage has been destroyed,

772
00:35:35,110 --> 00:35:37,630
and the two worlds can no longer connect.

773
00:35:38,590 --> 00:35:40,440
To travel from one realm to the other,

774
00:35:40,670 --> 00:35:42,670
you must cross the Sea of Flux.

775
00:35:43,550 --> 00:35:45,360
What is the Sea of Flux?

776
00:35:45,590 --> 00:35:47,400
I've never heard of it before.

777
00:35:48,280 --> 00:35:49,710
You can think of the Sea of Flux

778
00:35:49,710 --> 00:35:50,710
as a barrier,

779
00:35:51,590 --> 00:35:53,480
a wall that separates the heavens from the humans.

780
00:35:56,070 --> 00:35:57,000
So,

781
00:35:57,110 --> 00:35:58,710
if I can find a way

782
00:35:58,710 --> 00:35:59,760
to cross that wall,

783
00:35:59,880 --> 00:36:01,070
I can reach the Divine Realm

784
00:36:01,070 --> 00:36:02,000
and become a god?

785
00:36:02,000 --> 00:36:03,440
Theoretically, yes.

786
00:36:04,230 --> 00:36:06,320
But you shouldn't think about it.

787
00:36:06,880 --> 00:36:08,230
It's incredibly dangerous.

788
00:36:09,070 --> 00:36:10,280
Even gods,

789
00:36:10,550 --> 00:36:12,110
attempting to cross the Sea of Flux,

790
00:36:12,670 --> 00:36:14,320
face a life-or-death struggle.

791
00:36:14,510 --> 00:36:15,430
Why?

792
00:36:17,150 --> 00:36:18,550
Because it's a realm beyond the world,

793
00:36:19,510 --> 00:36:21,360
untethered by the laws of heaven and earth.

794
00:36:22,430 --> 00:36:24,200
How do you know so much about it?

795
00:36:33,880 --> 00:36:34,960
Can you see it now?

796
00:36:38,550 --> 00:36:39,360
Is it better?

797
00:36:42,320 --> 00:36:43,190
How does it feel?

798
00:36:43,590 --> 00:36:44,440
Are you alright?

799
00:36:48,880 --> 00:36:49,710
It's fine,

800
00:36:50,230 --> 00:36:51,510
just a little sting.

801
00:36:52,000 --> 00:36:52,960
I've just applied the medicine.

802
00:36:53,710 --> 00:36:54,960
It'll feel better in a couple of days.

803
00:36:55,920 --> 00:36:57,800
Today, I checked your wound.

804
00:36:58,760 --> 00:36:59,920
The others are healing well,

805
00:37:00,800 --> 00:37:02,280
but the knife wound on your chest

806
00:37:02,280 --> 00:37:03,400
hasn't fully healed yet.

807
00:37:04,760 --> 00:37:06,440
I heard from Qian Lin about that knife.

808
00:37:06,840 --> 00:37:07,670
It's called

809
00:37:07,840 --> 00:37:09,230
the God-Slaying Dagger,

810
00:37:09,360 --> 00:37:10,510
and it's quite sinister.

811
00:37:11,000 --> 00:37:12,510
You need to take extra care of yourself.

812
00:37:14,320 --> 00:37:15,320
Don't worry,

813
00:37:16,000 --> 00:37:17,760
I have the Divine Left Hand.

814
00:37:18,160 --> 00:37:20,330
I can heal any injury.

815
00:37:23,030 --> 00:37:24,630
I'll go prepare the medicine for you now.

816
00:37:27,070 --> 00:37:28,030
Thank you.

817
00:37:28,670 --> 00:37:30,000
If it hadn't been for you,

818
00:37:31,230 --> 00:37:32,000
I honestly don't know

819
00:37:32,000 --> 00:37:33,070
what I would have done.

820
00:37:34,510 --> 00:37:36,030
You're saying this all of a sudden.

821
00:37:36,190 --> 00:37:37,760
I'm not quite used to it.

822
00:37:39,360 --> 00:37:40,710
What's so strange about it?

823
00:37:41,360 --> 00:37:42,670
I'm simply telling the truth.

824
00:37:44,400 --> 00:37:45,480
I'll go prepare the medicine now.

825
00:38:23,370 --> 00:38:24,520
Can you still hold on?

826
00:38:26,760 --> 00:38:28,510
Where is Taihe's body?

827
00:38:28,760 --> 00:38:30,240
Didn't you see it?

828
00:38:30,260 --> 00:38:31,860
That was just an illusion from the Luofu Sea.

829
00:38:31,920 --> 00:38:33,190
It wasn't Taihe at all.

830
00:38:33,190 --> 00:38:34,920
Where exactly is Taihe?

831
00:38:37,840 --> 00:38:39,400
Did you scheme against Tanyin,

832
00:38:39,400 --> 00:38:40,760
causing her to lose her divine bone?

833
00:38:40,760 --> 00:38:41,510
Shut up!

834
00:38:42,300 --> 00:38:43,490
Don't mention her to me.

835
00:38:44,000 --> 00:38:45,250
That good-for-nothing,

836
00:38:45,710 --> 00:38:46,880
worthless girl,

837
00:38:47,700 --> 00:38:49,260
for the sake of some man,

838
00:38:49,670 --> 00:38:51,280
she not only abandoned Taihe,

839
00:38:51,640 --> 00:38:53,120
but also neglected herself.

840
00:38:53,670 --> 00:38:54,480
Tell me,

841
00:38:54,480 --> 00:38:55,710
why has this happened?

842
00:38:56,110 --> 00:38:57,510
She has practiced for so many years,

843
00:38:57,510 --> 00:38:58,760
with such great talent.

844
00:38:58,760 --> 00:38:59,880
She could have focused on her cultivation,

845
00:38:59,880 --> 00:39:00,710
made further progress,

846
00:39:00,710 --> 00:39:01,230
and lived a peaceful life,

847
00:39:01,230 --> 00:39:02,880
doing what she loves,

848
00:39:02,880 --> 00:39:04,480
enjoying longevity with the heavens, earth, and sun.

849
00:39:04,480 --> 00:39:05,510
But instead,

850
00:39:05,630 --> 00:39:06,590
she chose to become

851
00:39:06,590 --> 00:39:08,280
a despised mouse,

852
00:39:08,280 --> 00:39:09,480
chased by others,

853
00:39:09,480 --> 00:39:10,800
burned in blazing flames,

854
00:39:10,800 --> 00:39:12,590
hated by all!

855
00:39:15,030 --> 00:39:16,280
If you truly care for her,

856
00:39:16,590 --> 00:39:18,320
why did you hurt her?

857
00:39:18,320 --> 00:39:19,150
It's not me!

